{"tid":2049160,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍韜文：曾與五眼聯盟商討分擔接收港人可能性","createTime":"2020-06-03T09:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T16:51:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8f17c8a361488984e449882ac4a285bebaebdd4f","tid":2049160,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T09:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1529960_1_L_20200603154544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1529960_1_L_20200603154544.jpg&h=7ebe5cd6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國外相藍韜文與同屬「五眼聯盟」的美國、加拿大、澳洲及新西蘭代表，就中國問題上進行協調。藍韜文透露，曾經商討北京在落實港區國安法後，五國分擔接收港人的可能性。<br />\n<br />\n藍韜文早前呼籲中國停止制訂港區國家安全法，否則英國將改變對英國國民海外護照BNO的安排。<br />\n<br />\n首相約翰遜在《南華早報》撰文，表示如果北京落實推行「港區國安法」，英國政府已經準備好更改移民政策，允許BNO護照持有人，延長到英國的簽證至12個月，及在當地工作，以便港人取得公民資格。他又在英國《泰晤士報》撰文，強調不能迴避對港人的義務。"},{"pid":"0a9b30a67b1541de046e4f6c03ffb075db36735d","tid":2049160,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:45:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529960-20200603.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529960-20200603.htm&d=ZttPR3oQiG8LQafLEcup%2BGAbrlwo3OpfDsLQU8t9Jac%3D&h=fb3ccb5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1529960-20200603.htm&h=531b1cc4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1529960-20200603.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1efd2ee583efd37aa650192bc5b0e8e910158648","tid":2049160,"uid":114014,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T09:49:43.000Z","msg":"其實，都仍然係想留喺香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ddb97987e8e2f6e12126138b8ad6f0ad41dbe8d","tid":2049160,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T14:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f